===Verb===
{{en-verb|rewinds|rewinding|rewound}}

# To [[wind]] [[back]]; as, to rewind a [[VCR]], [[cassette]] [[tape]], or [[DVD]].
# To wind [[again]]; as, to rewind an unwound [[spool]] of [[string]] or [[tape]].

